commits.message: payment options added to account details
user can add and delete payment types
user can only access the Payment Types page if they are logged in
changed how authorization is checked on the payment type page
created product controller and views. Added some image uploading feature to the product create view. Create is currently not submitting form data to the database.

Merge pull request #41 from Remarkable-Donkeys/mw-productCreation

Mw product creation
only the current users payment types are show on the payment type page
updated payment type model to have an active property. the index will only show active payment types.

Merge pull request #42 from Remarkable-Donkeys/order-controller

created order controller

Merge pull request #43 from Remarkable-Donkeys/kn-paymentType

Kn add payment type
list of products only includes those created by the logged in user and are still set to active (status=true)
if user deletes a payment type that was used on a completed order then the active status of that payment type is set to false, else the payment type is deleted from the database
order lists are now only including orders of the currently logged in user
added ability to remove products, either completely from the database if not on any orders or by setting the status property of the product to false which in effect makes the product inactive
seeded database with payment types, orders, and orderproducts so that they payment type delete method can be tested
